---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' });
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="RecastCalc terms of service. Calculator results are estimates, not financial advice."
>
  <article class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 py-16 prose-recast">
    <h1 class="text-display-1 font-display font-semibold mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <h2>Acceptance</h2>
    <p>
      By using RecastCalc, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Not financial advice</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Calculator results are estimates only.</strong> RecastCalc is not a lender, mortgage
      broker, financial advisor, real estate professional, attorney, or tax professional. Nothing on
      this site constitutes personalized financial, legal, tax, or investment advice. Consult
      appropriately credentialed professionals before making decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      We make reasonable efforts to keep calculator math correct and lender data current, but we
      make no warranty as to accuracy, completeness, or fitness for a particular purpose. Lender
      policies change frequently and may differ from what's published here. Always verify
      directly with your lender before acting.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site are affiliate links. We may earn a commission if you click and
      complete an action on the destination site. Affiliate relationships do not influence
      calculator math or comparison logic. All affiliate links are tagged with
      <code>rel="sponsored nofollow"</code> and labeled "Sponsored".
    </p>

    <h2>Liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the fullest extent permitted by law, RecastCalc, its operator (Marcon Groupe LLC), and its
      affiliates are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or
      special damages arising from use of this site or reliance on calculator results. Use at
      your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these terms periodically. Continued use of the site after changes are posted
      constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Governing law</h2>
    <p>
      These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida, USA.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions: <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
